
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/landing.css">
</head>
<body>
    <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <div class="hero-text">
                <div class="hero-badge">
                    <i data-lucide="shield"></i>
                    <span>Early Warning System</span>
                </div>
                <h1 class="hero-title">
                    Preventing
                    <span class="gradient-text">Water-Borne</span>
                    Disease Outbreaks
                </h1>
                <p class="hero-description">
                    AI-powered health surveillance system that protects vulnerable communities in 
                    Northeastern India by detecting patterns, monitoring water quality, and 
                    enabling rapid response to prevent disease outbreaks.
                </p>
                
                <div class="hero-buttons">
                    <button class="btn btn-primary btn-large">
                        <a href="/login">Get Started</a>
                        <i data-lucide="arrow-right"></i>
                    </button>
                    <button class="btn btn-secondary btn-large">View Demo</button>
                </div>

                <div class="hero-features">
                    <div class="feature-item">
                        <i data-lucide="map-pin"></i>
                        <span>Serving NER Communities</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-divider"></div>
                    <span>Real-time Monitoring</span>
                    <div class="feature-divider"></div>
                    <span>AI-Powered Predictions</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="hero-visual">
                <div class="dashboard-mockup">
                    <div class="dashboard-card">
                        <h3>Disease Prevention Dashboard</h3>
                        <div class="dashboard-grid">
                            <div class="metric-card green">
                                <p class="metric-label">Water Quality</p>
                                <p class="metric-value">Safe</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="metric-card yellow">
                                <p class="metric-label">Risk Level</p>
                                <p class="metric-value">Medium</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="metric-card blue">
                                <p class="metric-label">Active Cases</p>
                                <p class="metric-value">12</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="metric-card purple">
                                <p class="metric-label">Alerts</p>
                                <p class="metric-value">2</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="overview">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header">
            <h2>Comprehensive Health Protection</h2>
            <p>Our integrated platform combines mobile technology, artificial intelligence, 
            and community engagement to create a robust early warning system for water-borne diseases.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="features-grid">
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon blue">
                    <!-- <i data-lucide="smartphone"></i> -->
                     <img width = "45px" src="/images/mobile-data.svg" alt="" srcset="">
                </div>
                <h3>Mobile Data Collection</h3>
                <p>Health workers and community volunteers collect data via mobile apps and SMS, ensuring comprehensive coverage even in remote areas.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon teal">
                    <img width = "45px" src="/images/ai.svg" alt="" srcset="">
                </div>
                <h3>AI Outbreak Prediction</h3>
                <p>Advanced machine learning models analyze symptoms, water quality, and seasonal patterns to predict potential disease outbreaks.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon cyan">
                    <img width = "45px" src="/images/water-drop.svg" alt="" srcset="">
                </div>
                <h3>Water Quality Monitoring</h3>
                <p>Integration with IoT sensors and test kits to continuously monitor water source contamination and safety parameters.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon orange">
                    <img width = "45px" src="/images/alert.svg" alt="" srcset="">
                </div>
                <h3>Real-time Alerts</h3>
                <p>Instant notifications to district health officials and local governance bodies when outbreak risks are detected.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon green">
                    <img width = "45px" src="/images/language.svg" alt="" srcset="">
                </div>
                <h3>Multilingual Support</h3>
                <p>Community interface available in local tribal languages with offline functionality for areas with limited connectivity.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon purple">
                   <img width = "45px" src="/images/analytics.svg" alt="" srcset="">
                </div>
                <h3>Analytics Dashboard</h3>
                <p>Comprehensive visualization tools for health departments to track hotspots, monitor interventions, and allocate resources effectively.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
</body>
</html>
